            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> by the removal of the `channel->streamtype != kChannelStreamProc` condition.\n\nThat condition is fragile, if the TUI ever needs to spawn another process. OTOH it's probably good to keep the TUI extremely simple, so it shouldn't be spawning other processes.\n\nBut it's probably more readable and reliable to set some sort of flag (similar to `Channel.detach`) on the channel, in any case.",
